    <note type="biography">
        <p>French scientist and writer. Doctor of medicine, Montpellier, 1841. Professor, École de pharmacie, Paris, 1853. From 1856, devoted himself to the popularisation of science. Editor and publisher of <hi rend="italic">L’Année scientifique</hi>, 1857–94. Prolific author of scientific works, and a pioneer of scientific theatre.</p></note>
